<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><atom:link href="jgood.io" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><title>JGood</title><link>jgood.io</link><description>Personal blog</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2020 16:07:17 -0500</lastBuildDate><generator>clj-rss</generator><item><guid>jgood.io/posts-output/2020-01-26-expo-shadow-cljs-starter/</guid><link>jgood.io/posts-output/2020-01-26-expo-shadow-cljs-starter/</link><title>A template for Expo apps with Shadow CLJS</title><description>&lt;h1 id="summary"&gt;Summary&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;This &lt;a href='https://github.com/jgoodhcg/shadow-cljs-expo-starter'&gt;repo&lt;/a&gt; is a template for &lt;a href='https://expo.io/'&gt;Expo&lt;/a&gt; projects using &lt;a href='https://shadow-cljs.github.io/docs/UsersGuide.html'&gt;Shadow CLJS&lt;/a&gt;. By cloning this repo and following the starter instructions in the &lt;a href='https://github.com/jgoodhcg/shadow-cljs-expo-starter#new-project-starter'&gt;readme&lt;/a&gt; you will be all setup to starting making a cross platform native app using Clojure.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h1 id="benefits"&gt;Benefits&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project has an opinionated set of all the necessary dependencies for an expo project written in cljs. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Staple libraries &lt;a href='https://github.com/redplanetlabs/specter'&gt;Specter&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href='https://github.com/metosin/spec-tools'&gt;Spec-tools&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href='https://clj-commons.org/camel-snake-kebab/'&gt;Camel-snake-kebab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='https://github.com/day8/re-frame'&gt;Re-frame&lt;/a&gt; for state management&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unit tests for re-frame handlers and subscriptions using shadow-cljs &lt;a href='https://shadow-cljs.github.io/docs/UsersGuide.html#target-node-test'&gt;node tests configuration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='https://circleci.com/'&gt;CircleCI&lt;/a&gt; setup for unit tests (no expo build or publishing yet)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='https://dependabot.com/'&gt;Dependabot&lt;/a&gt; for javascript deps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A nice &lt;a href='https://callstack.github.io/react-native-paper/getting-started.html'&gt;component library&lt;/a&gt; with an example of &lt;a href='https://github.com/jgoodhcg/shadow-cljs-expo-starter/blob/master/src/main/new_project_name/app.cljs#L50-L53'&gt;toggling dark mode&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="./../../img/shadow-cljs-expo-starter-dark-sm.png" alt="img" title="App in dark mode" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2020 00:00:00 -0500</pubDate></item><item><guid>jgood.io/posts-output/2019-07-21-hello-world/</guid><link>jgood.io/posts-output/2019-07-21-hello-world/</link><title>Hello World</title><description>&lt;p&gt;(:&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2019 00:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>